name: Cube Necklace Medium
description:
This Cube necklace is inspired by a Rubiks cube  part of the atomic collection.  White and black mother of pearl (cubes measures 13cm x 6cm  with a  50cm sterling silver chain).  Inlaid by hand.

The Atomic Collection was inspired by Crystallography, the experimental science of the arrangement of atoms in solids based on their geometry. This involves measuring the angles of crystal faces relative to theoretical reference axes (crystallographic axes), and establishing the symmetry of the crystal in question. This collection represents another way of enjoying the intrinsic beauty of a crystalline object, using graphics, wood and mother of pearl inlay.

shipped using Royal Mail Next day delivery
